      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Presenting an investment-grade E46 M3, featuring the high-revving S54 inline-six engine equipped with individual throttle bodies and a perfectly calibrated VANOS system. This example is mechanically impeccable, with documented preventative maintenance including rod bearing replacement and a comprehensive rear subframe reinforcement. The Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox offers precise throw and tactile feedback, sending power through a factory-spec limited-slip differential with no discernible lash. The chassis retains its original rigidity, supported by fresh bushings and an uncompromised suspension geometry. The exterior finish remains in concours state with exceptional depth, while the interior preserves the factory tactile matte surfaces and pristine leather bolsters. A truly turn-key specimen for the technical purist.",
